      "v3_sendB": "Voice 3 SEND B (0..1) — how much of voice 3 is tapped to aux bus B (→ reverb). CV via the v3_sendB input.",
      "v3_shape": "Voice 3 SHAPE (0..1) — the voice's waveshape/timbre morph. CV via the v3_shape input.",
